<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Sarig</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-08-18 20:32:51</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I am not a ranger but have accomplished this quest. For those non-rangers who may lack factions for this quest I'll list a couple helpful hints:<BR>
<BR>
Treant Heart:To get Jyle faction give about 100 muffins (3 at a time not stacked) to the guardian dwarf that is just outside Jyle's room. Then try giving Jyles lanterns.<BR>
<BR>
Fairie dust: Faction (unless you are KOS) plays no part in getting the fairie dust. I was dubious and handed over the wing. I was rewarded with the dust and faction returned to indifferent.<BR>
<BR>
So for those who have been slighted when handing items over to quest npcs with low factions, do not let that stop you doing this quest.</font></td></tr></table>
